    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>No it does not.\nAs per the <a href=\"https://mail.openjdk.java.net/pipermail/jdk8u-dev/2020-July/012143.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">release notes for openjdk8u262</a>, it is supported in OpenJDK 8 update 262.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>New features - <a href=\"https://bugs.openjdk.java.net/browse/JDK-8223147\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">JDK-8223147</a>: JFR Backport</p>\n</blockquote>\n"
