  "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/questions/61333887/does-openjdk-1-8-0-242-support-java-flight-recorder",
  "title" : "Does OpenJDK 1.8.0_242 support Java Flight Recorder?",
  "body" : "<p>I want to run a Java application with JFR enabled. When I start my application as below</p>\n<pre class=\"lang-bash prettyprint-override\"><code>java -XX:+UnlockCommercialFeatures -XX:StartFlightRecording\n</code></pre>\n<p>I get the following error:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Unrecognized VM option 'UnlockCommercialFeatures'</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Does OpenJDK 1.8.0_242 support Java Flight Recorder?</p>\n<p>The build is 1.8.0_242-b07.</p>\n"
